<div type="translation" resp="part:emfr">
                
<p n="1">Prosperity! Fortune!</p>
                
<p n="1">Seventeenth year of the king Parakesarivarman.</p>
                
<p>In this year 
<gap reason="lost" /> 
<supplied reason="lost">in the</supplied> Uṟattū
<supplied reason="lost">rkkūṟṟam</supplied> 
<gap reason="lost" /> 
<supplied reason="subaudible">there is</supplied> one 
<foreign>kaḻañcu</foreign> of gold that 
<gap reason="lost" /> gave for the 
<seg cert="low">Cattaṇam</seg>.</p>
                
<p n="2">This gold, as long as the moon and the sun, 
<gap reason="lost" /></p>
            </div>
            
         
